    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>A 41-year-old retired soldier who invites the investigators to his farm for the winter. He is newly married to a wealthy native woman (Carra) and has settled in the valley. Drinks wine and beer, occasionally indulges in battle cries. Initially unaware of the true supernatural nature of the farm's problems.</em></p>\n<p><strong>Role:</strong> ally\n | <strong>Occupation:</strong> Retired Legionary (Legio VI Victrix)\n</p><hr/>\n<table><tr>\n<td><strong>STR</strong><br/>70</td>\n<td><strong>CON</strong><br/>75</td>\n<td><strong>SIZ</strong><br/>60</td>\n<td><strong>DEX</strong><br/>70</td>\n<td><strong>INT</strong><br/>60</td>\n<td><strong>POW</strong><br/>70</td>\n<td><strong>APP</strong><br/>55</td>\n<td><strong>EDU</strong><br/>45</td>\n</tr></table>\n<p><strong>HP:</strong> 13 | <strong>SAN:</strong> 60 | <strong>MP:</strong> 14</p>\n<p><strong>Skills:</strong> Climb 40, Dodge 45, Drive 40, Empire 45, Fight 70, Language (Other: Latin) 45, Language (Own: Brythonic) 45, Ride 45, Spot Hidden 55, Status 40, Tactics 40, Throw 45</p>\n<p><strong>Attacks:</strong></p><ul>\n<li>Attack: 65 — 1D8+3/1D2</li>\n<li>Attack: 70 — 1D6+1+DB</li>\n<li>Attack: 45 — 1D8/2D9 thrown</li>\n<li>Attack: 40 — 1D4+DB</li>\n</ul>",
